{"tid":2088562,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"球迷喊「利物浦萬歲」被截查 警察指煽動港獨","createTime":"2020-07-01T07:57:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T05:55:51.000Z","uid":34572,"like":295,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"79808a2113d6f5454df5e9fbf4bec5a09f418691","tid":2088562,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T07:57:06.000Z","msg":"（獨媒特約報導）港版《國安法》通過翌日，有網民和民主派號召於銅鑼灣遊行至中環，下午1時許，警方已於銅鑼灣多次要求在場人士離開，並拉起多條封鎖線截查多人，更一度圍封銅鑼灣站出口，截查站內市民。<br />\n<br />\n期間有身穿利物浦球衣的男子於對面行人路高呼「利物浦萬歲！」身旁有人歡呼和應，防暴即衝前喝斥：「邊個煽動？」然後將男子帶進封鎖線截查。有圍觀者怒稱：「成班軍隊！」、「阿sir冇睇英超？」<br />\n<br />\n屈先生遭截查十分鐘後獲放行，他向記者表示，自己是三十年利物浦球迷，得知利物浦第一次於英超奪冠非常興奮，吃完飯在街上遇到其他球迷，「有感而發」便喊起「利物浦萬歲」，不明為何被警察反指違反《公安條例》、更稱他煽動港獨。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/50063781348_2b83cb5483_z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F65535%2F50063781348_2b83cb5483_z.jpg&h=3eb8e1fb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a7231f29df62f67a84fcb73a5707367a23c2fd64","tid":2088562,"uid":334957,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T07:58:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49b89d6a57461765bc6a5ce78c9d6b9dd066544b","tid":2088562,"uid":206337,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T07:58:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e831770ac74152bbb4e73bc